\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"明明好直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote>我簡短講句<br />\n彭斯話中國100年前比人打.美國無搶過任何中國既土地<br />\n而且比錢中國去建設.但自中共成立後.大家由同盟國變成敵人<br />\n<br />\n仲話中國應該走鄧小平改革開放果條路.而唔係習近平果條不歸路<br />\n<br />\n然後好似當年德國咁.不停指責中共點樣想入侵美國<br />\n中共有幾邪惡.以美國人係絕對唔會怕<br />\n<br />\n而且講到美國既軍費係有史以黎最高.仲準備建太空軍<br />\n又講到中共同中國人係應該分開</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:16:29.000Z","msg":"咁當年唔幫國民黨滅共，又無得好講啦。如果依家係中華民國統治，可能仲係盟友"},{"pid":"f3bf24a786b6a53646640dfc497623c7126e727a","tid":849452,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:38:27.000Z","msg":"即係話會搞意氣之爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7718eeffd2954defcc4756bdc4d4e6290035fd89","tid":849452,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"束手無策<br />\n束手待斃"},{"pid":"5d0ef63e305b5dc4bfe9f3c1f706fff695d76413","tid":849452,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T00:45:28.000Z","msg":"沉著氣，中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62426c6faa2a92af522b564aff61372f1aff386d","tid":849452,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T00:51:12.000Z","msg":"不打了不打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ab193347f46450c3accdd781bff8bcce72977c","tid":849452,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T00:51:42.000Z","msg":"成日當人地都係口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打完鋼鐵關稅<br />\n北韓<br />\n土耳其<br />\n500億關稅<br />\n2000億關稅<br />\n北美貿易協議<br />\n南韓<br />\n歐盟<br />\n日本<br />\n台灣旅行法<br />\n<br />\n都仲未醒，仍然覺得美國9up<img